title: 820-00281 - Liquid damage
message:
hey guys, i have a small question, 

the damaged capacitor is C9300 ( 22UF 20% 10V X5R-CERM 0603-1)

can i replace it with a higher voltage rating?

For example 22UF 20% 25V

Just double checking, i could not find a capacitor with the specifics of the bad capacitor, dont have a donor board for touch bar yet.

Appreciate the help!

title: 820-00281 - Liquid damage
message:
If is same size 0603, no problem.
You can use even bigger size; sometime is bit more dificult to solder it.
The most important is the capacity, not the size; and nominal voltage, of course
